a12b4c673684"],

Cell["\<\
This notebook reproduces Table 1 and Figure 4 from the article . 
It uses the symmetric - pair iteration for t_i = 0.23 and the full - grid \
symmetrization for the discrete symmetric profiles . 

Before using this notebook, evaluate 00 _LoadProject . nb so that the package \
is loaded .
  \
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{
  3.982769250755417*^9, {3.9827692839879208`*^9, 
